{%- layout none -%}
{%- comment -%}
  Alternate search view used by the Rimix Product Badges app (`?view=rmpb`).

  Rimix fetches /search(.js)?q=...&view=rmpb to resolve each card's product data
  (tags / inventory / sale state) and decide which badge to show. It queries by
  EITHER handle:"a" OR handle:"b"...  OR  title:"A" OR title:"B"...  depending on
  the app's RMPB_USE_TITLE setting. The response must be a pure JSON array.

  Two resolution paths, because they have very different reliability:

  1) handle: query  -> EXACT all_products[handle] lookup. No result cap, no fuzzy
     matching. Every requested product resolves. THIS IS THE RELIABLE PATH — set
     Rimix to match by product handle if you can.

  2) title: query  -> there is no exact "find product by title" in Liquid, so we
     fall back to search.results, which is relevance-RANKED and PAGINATED. With a
     big batch (~20 titles) Shopify's default page returns only ~10 results and
     mixes in fuzzy look-alikes, so real products get pushed out and their card
     shows no badge (that was the "first New Arrivals card has no badge" bug).
     We `paginate ... by 50` to lift the cap so far more requested products fit.
     Still not guaranteed for very large/ambiguous batches — prefer handle mode.
{%- endcomment -%}
[
{%- assign emitted = 0 -%}
{%- assign terms = search.terms -%}
{%- if terms contains 'handle:' -%}
    {%- assign handles = terms | replace: 'handle:"', '' | replace: '"', '' | replace: 'OR', ',' | split: ',' -%}
    {%- for h in handles -%}
        {%- assign handle = h | strip -%}
        {%- assign product = all_products[handle] -%}
        {%- if product != empty and product.id -%}
            {%- if emitted > 0 -%},{%- endif -%}
            {%- assign emitted = emitted | plus: 1 -%}
            {% render 'rmpb-product', product: product %}
        {%- endif -%}
    {%- endfor -%}
{%- else -%}
    {%- paginate search.results by 50 -%}
        {%- for product in search.results -%}
            {%- if product.object_type == 'product' -%}
                {%- if emitted > 0 -%},{%- endif -%}
                {%- assign emitted = emitted | plus: 1 -%}
                {% render 'rmpb-product', product: product %}
            {%- endif -%}
        {%- endfor -%}
    {%- endpaginate -%}
{%- endif -%}
]
